(38, 'Library', 'A library is an important asset for any center of higher learning which provides services and facilities to meet the requirements of learning, teaching, research & development and consultancy programs. Hence, efforts are always directed towards creating a very rich library having all important National and International journals/ newspapers, encyclopedia and magazines. The institution houses two libraries: Main library and Reference library. These libraries are a physical manifestation of our vision to distinguish the college as a center of resource in the knowledge era. The libraries aim to fulfill the crucial role of supporting learning and teaching activities to all members of the Institute.\r\n\r\nWith a collection of close to 40,000 books in addition to thousands of journals and theses, the library is one of the best in the region. It has been our endeavor to provide both students and faculty with the best possible research material including the latest writings of management gurus, popular management texts, classical books on management and much more.\r\n', 'Library'),
(44, 'about Us', '<h3 class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ''open sans'', arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 20px;">Welcome to IERT, Allahabad</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<blockquote class="custom-quote" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: #a7c2d9; color: #333333; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ''open sans'', arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px;">We serve the society by training professionals who can be leaders in innovation, entrepreneurship, creativity and management.</h3>\r\n<p class="people" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: #444444; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.5;"><span class="name" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6091ba;">Vision</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><span class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px;">IERT, Allahabad</span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">IERT is an engineering institute situated at the holy city of Allahabad.</span>&nbsp;The institute imparts Degree Engineering, Diploma Engineering &amp; Post Diploma in Computer Application and Management courses.&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">IERT</span>&nbsp;has consistently produced great scholars and hence recognizing its potential the Government of UP awarded it Academic Autonomy for Diploma Engineering Courses.&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">The Degree Division is affiliated to UP Technical University, Lucknow.</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />The campus of&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">IERT</span>, Allahabad, India, spreads across 26.5 acres of vast land. The institute has well planned infrastructure, lush green gardens and well laid roads, along with equipped classrooms and state-of-the-art laboratories. The campus features an auditorium which has been the epic center of all the festivals and functions, held at the institution. It has been the hosting ground to every function, from the recreational Freshers'' parties to the emotional Farewell speeches. In addition to auditorium, there is a well-furnished air-conditioned seminar hall where important meetings and seminars take place. The institute has food courts providing quality food at subsidized rates.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />Earlier,&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">IERT</span>&nbsp;used to provide diploma courses only.&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">In the year 2001, AICTE and State Govt. of U.P. upgraded this institute to Degree level to award Engineering degrees as well. Currently, the Institution is affiliated to UPTU, Lucknow.&nbsp;</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />The faculty at&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">IERT</span>&nbsp;is well-qualified and one of the best among the other Engineering Institutes of the region. The Institute provides more than 50,000 books and journals including latest technical magazines. Workshops and seminars of various fields are held at regular intervals which enhances the practical as well as theoretical knowledge of the students.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />Distinguished teachers from the most prestigious institutes of India, including MNNIT (Allahabad), JK Institute of Applied Physics (Allahabad) are invited as guest faculty.&nbsp;<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />Facilities available in&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">IERT</span>&nbsp;includes:</p>\r\n<ul class="custom-list-style" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #333333; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21.4286px;">\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">4 MBPS leased line with 24 hours of connectivity</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">More than 200 computers with IBM PROLAN Server</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">A separate CAD/CAM Lab for Industrial Production Branch</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Well-stocked libraries (Central Library &amp; Reference Library)</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Special emphasis on providing the students with practical knowledge</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Guest Faculty</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Industrial exposure through various Industrial Tours and Seminars</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Extra-curricular activities to promote all-round development</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Active participation in sporting events (in town or out of town)</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Hostel facilities</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Student Welfare Office for welfare of students</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 5px;">Classrooms with proper light, ventilation and furniture</li>\r\n</ul>', 'about'),
(45, 'History', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;"><img class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" src="http://iert.org.in/assets/images/750x300-about.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">In 1955, Civil Engineering School was opened by a society named " Institute of Engineering &amp; Technology ". Late Shanker Saran, retired judge Hon''able High Court of Allahabad and Late Vishwamitra an advocate were respectively the President and Secretary of the society. This school was self sustaining it''s actvities. A good number of students were admitted every year. The students were awarded two years'' Diploma in Civil Engineering Course by the Board of Engineering College.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">In 1962 U.P. Government took over this Institute by constituting a registered society named " Allahabad Engineering Polytechnic, Allahabad. "</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">The society constituted a Board of Management/Managing Committee constituting of 11 members to manage affairs of the Polytechnic. The state government awarded the status of Grant in Aid to the Institute. The rules and by-laws of the society were accordingly framed and the Director of Technical Education, U.P. became ex-officio Secretary of Management Committee.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">Reviewing the multifarious activities and the achievments of the Institute in the country and abroad, the U.P. Government changed the name of Allahabad Polytechnic to"Institute of Engineering and Rural Technology (I.E.R.T) " in 1982 and designated the post of "Director" in place of Principal, and the Institute was simultaneously awarded the Academic Autonomy. An Autonomy Committee was constituted and Secretary Technical Education, U.P. became ex-officio Chairman of the committee.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">The Institute Of Engineering and Rural Technology Allahabad (IERT) was established in 1955.In the year 1962 it became the institution of the State under Grant in Aid. Subsequently in the year 1982 the Institute was awarded Academic Autonomy by the State Government. The governance of the institution remains under the predominant control of the State.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">The institution had already established itself as a premier institution : rather the best among the very best in the country in diploma engineering programs. The institute maintains the same position.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">The Engineering Degree Division of the Institute Of Engineering and Rural Technology, Allahabad was set up in 2001,when the college started offering degree courses in engineering with affiliation from U.P. Technical University , Lucknow (UP). It started it''s academic activities from October 2001 with the first batch joining the college on 30th October 2001. The Institute has a highly developed educational infrastructure and good faculty with an international outlook. The Institute aims to have a very active interaction with the industry and has a mission to serve society by training professionals who can be leaders in innovation, entrepreneurship, creativity and management.</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #444444; font-size: 15px; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 21.4286px;">The infrastructure of iert is rapidly increasing the no. of seats in each branch has increased and facilities provided to students are increasing day by day.</p>', 'history'),
(48, 'Contact us', '<article class="contact-form col-md-8 col-sm-7  page-row">\r\n<h3 class="title">Get in touch</h3>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;d love to hear from you. text</p>\r\n<form>\r\n<div class="form-group name"><label for="name">Name</label> <input id="name" class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" /></div>\r\n<!--//form-group-->\r\n<div class="form-group email"><label for="email">Email<span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" class="form-control" type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" /></div>\r\n<!--//form-group-->\r\n<div class="form-group phone"><label for="phone">Phone</label> <input id="phone" class="form-control" type="tel" placeholder="Enter your contact number" /></div>\r\n<!--//form-group-->\r\n<div class="form-group message"><label for="message">Message<span class="required">*</span></label> <textarea id="message" class="form-control" rows="6" placeholder="Enter your message here..."></textarea></div>\r\n<!--//form-group--> <button class="btn btn-theme" type="submit">Send message</button></form></article>\r\n<!--//contact-form-->', 'contact'),
